Date: Sun, 8 Mar 2026 14:48:35 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 2/9] CRAN compliance: fix warnings in vendored sources

- Initialize variables in nauty to silence -Wmaybe-uninitialized
- Comment out diagnostic pragmas (CRAN flags these)
- Fix %zu/%zd format strings for Win64 portability (LLP64)
